quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,84,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! kaho ke"" hum Allah ko mantay hain, uss taleem ko mantay hain jo hum par nazil ki gayi hai, unn talemaat ko bhi mantay hain jo ibrahim, Ismael, ishaq, yaqoob aur aulaad yaqoob par nazil hui theen aur unn Hadayat par bhi imaan rakhtay hain jo( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)aur eesa aur dosray payghambaroon ko unn ke Rab ki taraf se di gayeen hum un ke darmain farq nahi karte aur hum Allah ke tabay farmaan ( muslim ) hain """
3,85,is farmaa bardari ( islam ) ke siwa jo shakhs koi aur tareeqa ikhtiyar karna chahay is ka woh tareeqa hargiz qubool nah kya jaye ga aur akhirat mein woh nakaam o namuraad rahay ga
3,86,kaisay ho sakta hai ke Allah unn logon ko hadaayat bakhshay jinhon ne Nemat imaan pa lainay ke baad phir kufar ikhtiyar kya halaank woh khud is baat par gawahi day chuke hain ke yeh rasool haq par hai aur un ke paas roshan nishanain bhi aa chuki hain Allah zaalmon ko to hadaayat nahi diya karta
3,87,un ke zulm ka sahih badla yahi hai ke un par Allah aur firshton aur tamam insanon ki phatkaar hai
3,88,"isi haalat mein woh hamesha rahen ge, nah un ki saza mein takhfeef hogi aur nah inhen mohlat di jaye gi"
3,89,"Albata woh log bach jayen ge jo iss ke baad tauba kar ke apne tarz amal ki islaah kar len, Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
3,90,"magar jin logon ne imaan laane ke baad kufar ikhtiyar kya, phir apne kufar mein barhatay chalay gay un ki tauba bhi qubool nah hogi, aisay log to pakkay gumraah hain"
3,91,"yaqeen rakho, jin logon ne kufar ikhtiyar kya aur kufar hi ki haalat mein jaan di unn mein se koi agar apne aap ko saza se bachanay ke liye roye zameen bhar kar bhi sona Fidya mein day to ussay qubool nah kya jaye ga aisay logon ke liye dard naak saza tayyar hai aur o hay apna koi madadgaar nah payen ge"
